## NLB-B — Internal, VPC-B (Palo Alto Sim)

```
Placement:   subnet-b-untrust (10.1.1.0/24), VPC-B
Type:        network (layer 4)
Scheme:      internal
Listeners:
  TCP 80  → Target Group → Palo TRUST ENI (10.1.2.10) port 80
  TCP 443 → Target Group → Palo TRUST ENI (10.1.2.10) port 443
```

Reachable from:

- VPC-A via TGW1 (A1 Chrome management browser validation)
- VPC-D via TGW2 (D1 simulated customer traffic)

NLBs have no security groups. Access controlled by:

- NACL on subnet-b-untrust
- Security Group on B1 TRUST ENI (allow from 10.1.1.0/24)

